*Pravcu* Vranja ide uži železnički put. (Towards Vranja there goes a narrow railway line.)

U pravcu Zaječara se nalazi planina. (In the direction of Zajecar there is a mountain.)

Vozeći *pravcu* Beograda, skrenite desno. (When driving towards Belgrade, turn right.)

Konji su jurili *pravcu* sela. (The horses were running towards the village.)

On je krenuo *pravcu* planine. (He started out towards the mountain.)